{"tid":888674,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【獨家踢爆】亞姐用Camilla做17直播 李芷菱認有女仔每月賺過百萬","createTime":"2018-11-04T03:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T05:03:09.000Z","uid":23731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3d99ed54beb129843f937bcd27a20ecf627001","tid":888674,"uid":23731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181104/634082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181104%2F634082&d=PA4%2BDzYEZCZIURZfFi40EAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=06bf2f29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181104%2F634082&h=1662bc35\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181104/634082</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年亞姐選舉復活，今年冠軍梁雪瑤同最上鏡小姐李芷菱都參選過港姐，原來大熱倒灶嘅李芷菱更加以Camilla喺17直播賺錢。李芷菱承認喺17直播平台做咗年幾，因為朋友覺得佢講說話有幽默感幾好笑而介紹。對於有指有女主播一個月賺過百萬，她一點也不奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n「過百萬其實好少事，我哋平台有啲主播都過一億，嗰啲真係收入不菲，但係有啲會少啲，所以都要睇彩數，睇吓有冇一班粉絲持同錫你。」她說。至於過百萬係指點數，即係粉絲會買模擬禮物送俾主播，禮物嘅點數，最後可以兌換現金，所以收過億點數禮物嘅主播，有成過百萬收入。"},{"pid":"db6dd2a4ed5bda71959542761f68fcdd099f8c52","tid":888674,"uid":33336,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"過億？精呀？"},{"pid":"166f79118660fe71001746e3be0a5413088494cd","tid":888674,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"唔係覺得有人信呀？"},{"pid":"18658445b3a18b53c52f0ef49f7d32185bf6b824","tid":888674,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db6dd2a4ed5bda71959542761f68fcdd099f8c52","tid":888674,"uid":33336,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"過億？精呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"笑到癲"},{"pid":"28f9d3ccdfc3b52d8c0822e9458e6dfc35dd26d1","tid":888674,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T05:03:09.000Z",